{"tid":1590810,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"TAFE係傳銷騙局？","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:22:09.000Z","uid":321421,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e86f19f115beb41196002070c2cc74620a697036","tid":1590810,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"小妹今年yr1，男友同我同年都係19DSE<br />\n男友英文1咗 依家喺旺角讀緊一間叫TAFE嘅嘢<br />\n我前幾日同佢溫書望一望佢啲教材，根本同F1,2嘅英文冇乜分別，我覺得佢俾人呃咗，唔知點幫佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話係考oral嗰時門口有個姐姐叫佢幫手填問卷，之後仲等佢考埋。唔知係我戒心重定點，我覺得個姐姐一定另有所圖，邊有咁好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後即刻上網就睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/200595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/200595</a><br />\n<br />\n間嘢係讀兩年top-up degree然後去澳洲讀技術學院，我覺得好似讀澳洲嘅IVE咁，大學都唔係<br />\n<br />\n我之前試過同佢講叫佢讀翻啲大路嘢<br />\n佢話嗰間嘢冇網上面講得咁差，比心機就得<br />\n但佢好似俾個姐姐洗腦咁，當個姐姐係指南針<br />\n淨係信矖個姐姐，覺得個姐姐唔會呃佢<br />\n我send咗好多報導話個集團專呃人錢<br />\n佢竟然同我講，話個姐姐點會呃佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個姐姐會得閒send啲相同佢講自己做緊咩，令佢放低戒心，好似真係有人幫自己咁<br />\n<br />\n有冇人話我知點先幫到佢，我好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理佢好似望住佢死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666470e62931af6491bd4e2b1eefee054f8edb46","tid":1590810,"uid":68689,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"有心讀書一定係讀八大asso 出名學店搵鬼讀咩"},{"pid":"ef36c210d1471ebd184bb3f12b41ac6710adbc12","tid":1590810,"uid":321421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"666470e62931af6491bd4e2b1eefee054f8edb46","tid":1590810,"uid":68689,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"有心讀書一定係讀八大asso 出名學店搵鬼讀咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"我同佢講過 話一年fd駁上去asso仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢好似俾條傳銷女洗咗腦咁，覺得澳洲就一定好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e935a416b4e23647de0b27d61fdfaeefcd51ea","tid":1590810,"uid":208823,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"又到放榜ge季節 見到hkue同UCHE千其唔好讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解提極都會有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca50d19287e85122188a01fb521b54ba949f62f","tid":1590810,"uid":321421,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0e935a416b4e23647de0b27d61fdfaeefcd51ea","tid":1590810,"uid":208823,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"又到放榜ge季節 見到hkue同UCHE千其唔好讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解提極都會有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"佢好似讀得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得廢過i大"},{"pid":"3ec2077116555bcb5d50bbbd46170cbf916253db","tid":1590810,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"TAFE間野 澳洲睇過啲環境 其實師資幾好 <br />\n不過唔知香港原來要咁樣轉過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fdcf70779579ae6aa72b42fac151ad0da59423","tid":1590810,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"TAFE呢個制度本身真係存在<br />\n但香港呢個係咪真就唔知"},{"pid":"56d9ac9ad3b49ca6acae7dd5cc8babd86dae6fa5","tid":1590810,"uid":72046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"分手<br />\n豬咁蠢"},{"pid":"a71cba9fdb86d0bb1eb1ea89acb2bf2a5ae6365f","tid":1590810,"uid":210825,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0